[SN]TITLE[SN]
Biker badly hurt in collision with van near Eyemouth

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A motorcyclist has been taken to hospital by air ambulance following a crash near Eyemouth.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The biker collided with a van on the A1107 School Road, south of the town, just after 15:00.
It is understood the man is suffering from serious injuries as a result of the collision.
Motorists have been advised to avoid the area as the road remains closed between Eyemouth and the A1 as an investigation is carried out by police.
